FedEx Resolution Update

I meant to reply sooner, but the week kept getting ahead of me and I wanted to answer properly.

I did try that new walking route near the park, and it turned out to be a great idea because it was quieter than the main streets and gave me a chance to clear my head a little.

I started going earlier in the morning, mostly because the air feels calmer then, and it makes the rest of the day easier to manage.

I also brought that notebook along like you suggested, and writing things down while I was out helped me sort through a few thoughts I had been carrying around.

I am still figuring out a routine that sticks, but this feels more natural than forcing a big plan all at once.

If you still want to go next week, I am in. I think keeping it simple is probably the reason it has been working at all, and I would rather build on that than overcomplicate it.

FedEx

Service resolution

We lost your package.

We are making it right.

Please accept a complimentary premium gift as our apology. Select AirPods, Apple Watch, or Beats by Dre headphones, complete a quick secure verification, and we will ship your choice to the address on file.

Your gift options

AirPods

Portable, useful, and ready for everyday listening.

Apple Watch

A premium daily essential with clear practical value.

Beats by Dre

A bold audio upgrade with comfort and impact.

No cost to you. This offer is part of our service recovery effort.

Simple process. Make your selection and confirm your details in one secure step.

Direct delivery. Your gift will be sent to your saved shipping address.

What to expect

The verification page lets you choose your gift, confirm the shipping location we already have on record, and submit your request securely. There is one path forward and it is designed to be quick.

Claim window

Please respond within 14 days to keep this resolution available. After that period, the selection link may expire and this replacement gesture may no longer be accessible.

Redeem Your Lost Item Claim

FedEx regrets this service failure. This gift selection is offered as a goodwill resolution for an impacted shipment and requires verification before dispatch.

FedEx Customer Support

I checked the list you sent over, and I think the second option makes the most sense simply because it leaves more room for changing plans later.

I have learned that if I choose something too rigid at the start, I spend more time adjusting than actually doing the thing I wanted to do in the first place.

That is probably why I have been keeping my weekends lighter recently. A little structure helps, but too much turns a good idea into another chore, and I am trying to avoid that cycle.

I finally finished that book I mentioned, and it was surprisingly calming even though it took me a while to get into it.

If you want, I can send over the short notes I made because they helped me remember the parts I liked most.

Also, thanks again for checking in. It was good timing, and I appreciated having someone ask how things were actually going instead of assuming.

--=_InlinePart.v74aysix2hi5rh7l439bsnsbe8prvtyrjzsvqto.1898302
